cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with reconstructing 3D shapes from 2D sketches using deep learning techniques. Additionally, the paper also involves graphics (cs.GR) as it converts the point cloud into a polygon mesh. The use of deep learning networks also suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper's focus on multi-view maps and optimization problems suggests that it could also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
